{"tid":2301050,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"絲打點睇啲畫本子嘅男仔?","createTime":"2020-11-26T04:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T01:44:29.000Z","uid":257428,"like":157,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"16bddb5dfb3b08330aa88c46e993e31dce06b111","tid":2301050,"uid":257428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"我同我朋友都因為疫情失業，有一日佢揾返我問我想唔想畫返畫，佢話畫完啲本子放去日本賣每月都有幾千蚊頂住先。<br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係，行左兩個月之後，佢唔小心比女朋友發現左佢偷偷地畫本子，覺得好嘔心叫佢唔好再畫。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地兩兄弟細細個就好鐘意畫畫，我嘅夢想係自己整隻驚出黎，美術program一腳踢 ; 佢嘅夢想係做漫畫家，但可惜正常漫畫競爭大，唔夠錢過活。結果我地都因為現實放棄左夢想，咁就過左10年，如今佢難得有機會再畫返畫，佢唔想咁快又放棄。<br />\n<br />\n我想知道絲打點睇啲畫本子嘅男仔，會唔會覺得好毒同好嘔心?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 接受唔到，知道左會分手"},{"pid":"07a014ab9ba17bcc27d9940596c0610d68ce29af","tid":2301050,"uid":2419,"like":22,"dislike":22,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"up乜鳩呀屌你老味"},{"pid":"9a231ec79d50991708decf8db9ad505d4d863d94","tid":2301050,"uid":52509,"like":9,"dislike":11,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"07a014ab9ba17bcc27d9940596c0610d68ce29af","tid":2301050,"uid":2419,"like":22,"dislike":22,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"up乜鳩呀屌你老味"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:14:01.000Z","msg":"本子即係同人H漫"},{"pid":"a3cf530d11a5c6197b01c63507dee9ec594c553e","tid":2301050,"uid":219466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"無乜問題呀"},{"pid":"3973a394b3486c9c7a5dc2e184eb25c116c9c0bc","tid":2301050,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"正呀支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754fcfb3091013d359383a06005e47b5d6b5c6a0","tid":2301050,"uid":299187,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"16bddb5dfb3b08330aa88c46e993e31dce06b111","tid":2301050,"uid":257428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":